  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This advanced form of the Raikiri technique allows the user to charge and shoot his Raikiri at the target in a zigzag formation that strikes with the same vital precision of its parent technique, but with more power. The user makes a ranged touch attack that deals 6d6+1 electricity damage and 4d4+1 sonic damage. If the user rolls a natural 20 on the touch attack, the target must succeed a Fortitude save or become stunned for 1 round afterwards.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Requires:</b> Raikiri (3)</p>\n<p><b>Empower:</b> The user may spend an additional 1 point of chakra to increase both the electricity and sonic damage by 1, up to 6d6+5 and 4d4+5.</p>\n",
